           {"neutral","Player: Greetings, my lord. May I speak with you for a moment?\\nCharacter: Oi, milord! Wot can I do fer ye today?\\nPlayer: I've come to discuss some issues concerning the village.\\nCharacter: Issues ye say? Wot kind o' issues?\\nPlayer: The villagers are in need of food and shelter.\\nCharacter: Aye, tis a difficult time fer us all. We've been hit hard by the drought and pests.\\nPlayer: I understand. I will see what I can do to help.\\nCharacter: Bless ye, milord. The villagers will surely be grateful."},
